{"an1.248:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 1 ","an1.248:0.2":"19. Chatthavagga ","an1.248:1.1":"“Etadaggam, bhikkhave, mama savakanam upasakanam pathamam saranam gacchantanam yadidam tapussabhallika vanija. ","an1.249:1.1":"… Dayakanam yadidam sudatto gahapati anathapindiko. ","an1.250:1.1":"… Dhammakathikanam yadidam citto gahapati macchikasandiko. ","an1.251:1.1":"… Catuhi sangahavatthuhi parisam sanganhantanam yadidam hatthako alavako. ","an1.252:1.1":"… Panitadayakanam yadidam mahanamo sakko. ","an1.253:1.1":"… Manapadayakanam yadidam uggo gahapati vesaliko. ","an1.254:1.1":"… Sanghupatthakanam yadidam hatthigamako uggato gahapati. ","an1.255:1.1":"… Aveccappasannanam yadidam surambattho. ","an1.256:1.1":"… Puggalappasannanam yadidam jivako komarabhacco. ","an1.257:1.1":"… Vissasakanam yadidam nakulapita gahapati”ti. ","an1.257:1.2":"Vaggo chattho. "}